{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready to dive into the <strong>ultimate sports showdown</strong> with <strong>BlastBall: All-Stars!</strong>\u00a0Choose your favorite all-star from our roster of cuddly creatures and jump into the action. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With simple, intuitive controls that <i>adapt to each sport</i>, hopping into any game is <strong>easy</strong>! Want to score <strong>highlight reel goals</strong> and feel like an All-Star? No problem. Use the <i>left stick to aim</i> and the <i>right stick to add spin</i>, and that\u2019s it. Each hit builds up your <i>blast meter</i>, letting you slow down time and unleash a <strong>blazing-fast shot</strong>! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Compete in simplified <strong>fan-favorite sports</strong> like soccer, dodgeball, gaga ball, tennis, volleyball, pickleball, and air hockey. Can\u2019t decide what to play first? Battle it out in a <i>multi-sport tournament</i> to prove who\u2019s the true champion! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Only have a few minutes to play? Get a match going <i>in less than 30 seconds</i>. Plus, you can customize the rules, guaranteeing non-stop fun for friends and family! Are you ready to be an All-Star?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you not sold yet? Play the <strong>FREE DEMO</strong> today!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170060/extras/couch.png?t=1738008520\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiplayer <strong>sports action</strong> for <strong>1-4 players</strong>\u00a0with favorites like\u00a0<strong><i>soccer</i></strong><i>, <strong>dodgeball</strong>, <strong>tennis</strong>, and <strong>air hockey</strong></i>.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170060/extras/soccer.gif?t=1738008520\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170060/extras/custom.png?t=1738008520\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Want to bend the rules? More power to you! Each game has unique settings that can be changed to mix things up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170060/extras/customize.gif?t=1738008520\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170060/extras/master.png?t=1738008520\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With simple, intuitive controls, hopping into any sport is easy! Utilize your blast charges and add spin to your shots to become a real All-Star!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170060/extras/tennis.gif?t=1738008520\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170060/extras/sports.png?t=1738008520\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Soccer, Air Hockey, Gagaball, Royalty, Dodgeball, Knockout, Volleyball, Tennis, Squash, Pickleball - and <strong>more to come!</strong>\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170060/extras/air_hockey.gif?t=1738008520\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170060/extras/crew.png?t=1738008520\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Becca, Reggie, Lance, and Blaire are ready to play with more friends on the way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170060/extras/IMG_285